title: Proposal to Boost the JGN-BNB farm and a New Syrup Pool
body:
#### PancakeSwap Welcomes Back Juggernaut ($JGN) to Syrup Pool!

CAKE holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from **Juggernaut ($JGN)**, a Metaverse NFT 2.0 project with a powerful DeFi Infrastructure, creating a cohesive and empowering ecosystem.

#### What is Boost?

Boost is basically an increase in farm multiplier over a set period of time, which is offered in exchange for additional tokens from the boosted project, which are then put into a new Syrup Pool!

So basically, the JGN-BNB farm will go to a 0.5x multiple for 7 days. Don’t worry, this will only cause temporary dilution among the other farms. At the same time, there will be a new $JGN Syrup Pool with 125,000 JGN tokens to be earned by staking CAKE.

#### The Syrup Pool:

Stake CAKE tokens to earn $JGN tokens!

- **Total Tokens:** 105,500 JGN
- **Distribution duration:** 7 days
- **Start time:** Approx. 11am UTC on November 11th 2021
- **Finish time:** Approx. 11am UTC on November 18th 2021
- **Token rewards per block:** 0.5233 JGN
    
#### Max Stake per wallet:

100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterward.

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some Syrup pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.

#### What is Juggernaut?

From the team: “Juggernaut (JGN) is leading the way to Metaverse NFT 2.0 with a powerful DeFi Infrastructure. JGN wants to achieve a cohesive intersection of DeFi, NFTs, and Metaverse, into a fun and consumer-grade experience.

The JGN ecosystem features a BSC NFT Exchange, JuggerWORLD, which is a globally leading and interconnected NFT exchange including user minting, royalty distribution. Moreover, DeFi infrastructure with governance, voting and unique membership benefits enable a more empowered user experience.
 
The upcoming JuggyLAND Metaverse brings an innovative market-first with Create-to-play: giving power back to players and the ecosystem. Experience a new level of connection and earn with the JGN User-Generated Metaverse.”

#### To learn more about Juggernaut, the chefs advise you to visit their official communication channels:

- **Website:** https://jgndefi.com/

[https://docs.pancakeswap.finance/products/syrup-pool/syrup-pool-guide](https://docs.pancakeswap.finance/products/syrup-pool/syrup-pool-guide)

#### BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

The official $JGN token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is: 

https://bscscan.com/token/0xc13b7a43223bb9bf4b69bd68ab20ca1b79d81c75

Any other $JGN token will be a scam. Always verify the token address before buying tokens. If you receive a $JGN token airdrop from another address, it’s probably a scam, and we advise you to ignore it.
